

	 
      Old man Mechling ran outside in a hurry and saw to his great dismay, a short little man was dancing around naked on his roof and urinating in the snow.  "GET DOWN FROM THERE!", he cried, but the little man was already out of site.  Months later, they met again at Dairy Queen.  Upon driving away, old man Mechling was mooned with a pressed ham on the window, the whole world watching, and Max was banned from the house for good.  This is a true story.
     
    
